\c 20
\s Maguta matanhatu eutiziro
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Joshua achiti:
\v 2 Taura kuvana vaIsraeri uti: Zvimisirei maguta eutiziro andakareva\x + Eki. 21.13. Num.. 35.6,11,14. Det. 19.2,3,4,5,6.\x* kwamuri neruoko rwaMozisi.
\v 3 Kuti muurayi anouraya munhu asiri maune asingazivi\x + 20.5.\x*\x + 20.9. Num.. 35.11.\x* atizireko. Zvino achava kwamuri utiziro pamutsivi weropa.
\v 4 Kana achitizira kune rimwe remaguta ayo, achamira pamukova wesuwo reguta\x + Rut. 4.1,2.\x*, uye achareva nyaya yake munzeve dzevakuru veguta iro; zvino vachamugamuchira kwavari muguta ndokumupa nzvimbo kuti agare pakati pavo.
\v 5 Zvino kana mutsivi weropa akamudzingirira, havangapi muurayi muruoko\x + Det. 32.30.\x* rwake, nokuti wakarova wekwake asingazivi, asina kumuvenga zuro\x + 20.3. Det. 4.42; 19.4.\x* \add na\add*marimwezuro.
\v 6 Zvino achagara muguta iro kusvika amira pamberi peungano kutongwa, kusvika\x + 20.9. Num.. 35.12,24.\x* pakufa kwemupristi mukuru achavapo\x + Num.. 35.25.\x* mazuva iwayo; ipapo muurayi achadzoka auye kuguta rake nekuimba yake, kuguta kwaakatiza achibva.
\p
\v 7 Zvino vakanatsa Kedheshi muGarirea\x + 19.37.\x* panyika yezvikomo yaNafutari, neShekemu panyika\x + 17.7.\x* yezvikomo yaEfuremu, neKiriyati-Aribha\x + 24.33.\x* rinova\x + 21.11. Ruk. 1.39.\x* Hebhuroni panyika yezvikomo yaJudha.
\v 8 Nemhiri kwaJoridhani paJeriko kumabvazuva vakapa Bhezeri murenje\x + Det. 4.43. Josh. 21.36. 1 Makor. 6.78.\x* pabani kubva kurudzi\x + Det. 3.10.\x* rwaRubheni, neRamoti muGiriyadhi kubva kurudzi rwaGadhi, neGorani\x + 21.38. 1 Madz. 22.3.\x* muBhashani kubva kurudzi rwaManase\x + Det. 4.43. Josh.21.27. 1 Makor. 6.71.\x*.
\v 9 Awa aiva maguta akamisirwa vana vose vaIsraeri nemutorwa agere pakati pavo semweni\x + Num.. 35.15.\x*, kuti ani nani anouraya munhu asiri maune atizireko, kuti arege\x + 20.3.\x* kufa neruoko rwemutsivi weropa, kusvika amira pamberi peungano\x + 20.6.\x*.